title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: An associates demands may prompt you to come up with an inventive solution today. You want to accommodate the valuable folks in your life while the service-oriented Virgo Moon moves through your 7th House of Relationships. However, its not helpful if youre so selfless that you undervalue your own needs. But the current dynamic doesnt require one person to have less just because the other has more. Talking openly about any competing desires can generate enough synergy to promote growth and satisfy you both.
